column2: SELECT m.specobjid, n.objid, m.ra_# AS ra1, m.dec_# AS dec1, p.ra AS RA, p.dec AS DEC, o.z as REDSHIFT, o.zerr AS REDSHIFTERR, into mydb.NewRedshifts from MyDB.large_z_diff AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN SpecObj AS o ON o.bestObjID = n.ObjID JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON p.objid = n.objid
